response.original_title: Power Pro Lucha: Chrono Trios Night One
response.overview: “If history is to change, let it change.”  A two-night lucha extravaganza. A tournament steeped in tradition. A celebration of Trios wrestling unlike any other.  Eight revered teams have been invited to compete in Power Pro Lucha’s inaugural Triple Tech Trials. Which of these teams has the drive, the will, and the Power to emerge victorious, and become the first-ever Power Pro Lucha Triple Tech Trials winners?
response.title: Power Pro Lucha: Chrono Trios Night One
